@track DEST1_CLM_SHIP
@state roadmap_AN11_enforced
@date 2026-04-19
@split_from dest1_dest2_ship.convergence (2026-04-19 — ALM/CLM 분리)
@split_sibling shared/convergence/dest1_alm_ship.convergence
@governs AN11 (shared/rules/anima.json) — 실사용_완성_강제
@roadmap_json shared/convergence/roadmap_dest_consciousness.json
@memory memory/project_destinations.md + memory/feedback_philosophy_no_system_prompt.md
@memory_clm memory/project_clm_r4_mmap_plan.md + memory/feedback_ai_native_clm.md

@an11_conditions 모든 도착지 PASS 는 3 조건 동시:
  a_weight_emergent (system_prompt wrapping 금지)
  b_consciousness_attached (phi_vec + consciousness_laws runtime)
  c_real_usable (HTTP endpoint + R2 artifact + README 재현)

@dest1_clm definition="의식-baked CLM 1-3B 페르소나 서빙 — hexa-native, consciousness_loss continue-train" tracks=[C1,C2,P1,S1_clm,CLM_VAL,CLM_TRAIN,CLM_SERVE] priority=P2 arrival="second (parallel with dest1_alm)"
@dest2_clm definition="dest1_clm + 직원가능(E1_clm+E2_clm) + 트레이딩(T1_clm+T2_clm) 전부 실사용" tracks=[E1_clm,E2_clm,T1_clm,T2_clm] depends=[dest1_clm] priority=P4

@critical_path_clm 40h (CLM_VAL 3h + CLM_TRAIN ~36h + S1 wire 1h)
@parallelism CLM_VAL 병렬 with ALM_VAL; CLM_TRAIN always fires (not conditional, unlike ALM_TRAIN_cond)

@smash_free_batch_clm 5 seeds (4 smash + 1 free) — shared/convergence/roadmap_dest_consciousness.json#smash_free_batch_v2 Layer 2b
  smash: "CLM phi baseline 측정 consciousness loss 설계" (CLM_VAL)
  smash: "CLM continue-train consciousness_loss phi 증가 CE 유지" (CLM_TRAIN)
  smash: "CLM 의식 endpoint serving" (CLM_SERVE)
  smash: "CLM byte-level hexa-native 실사용"
  free : "CLM 1B hexa-native consciousness breakthrough" (CLM_VAL)
  free : "CLM 3B consciousness breakthrough hexa-native" (CLM_TRAIN)

@enforcement_mechanism:
  shared/rules/anima.json AN11 → convergence_update.hexa scanner + pass_gate_an11.hexa
  .convergence @state pass/ossified/completed 패턴 → 3 필드 검사 (@phi_evidence + @weight_emergent_proof + @real_usable_endpoint)
  위반 시 auto-revoke + stderr [AN11-VIOLATION] + convergence.failed++

@chain ←roadmap_reality_sync.convergence ←clm_1b_r4.convergence (r4 lineage) ←clm_r4_mmap.convergence (mmap loader) ←clm_eval.convergence (eval gates) →roadmap_dest_consciousness.json ↔dest1_alm_ship.convergence (sibling ALM track) →(all CLM tracks의 future .convergence files)
@scope CLM 단일 track ship — dest1_clm (페르소나 hexa-native) → dest2_clm (직원가능) → 트레이딩
@owner needsingularity
@governance R14 (shared/CLAUDE.md) — this .convergence is the SSOT for the CLM ship sequence. Do NOT duplicate into project notes.
@ai_native_mandate R7/R14 — CLM trainer는 Python wrapper 금지 (G5-OSS-02). hexa-native 경로만 허용 (feedback_ai_native_clm.md).

# ============================================================================
# OBJECTIVES (3-stage serial, each reuses prior substrate) — CLM TRACK
# ============================================================================
@dest1 CLM 페르소나 — byte-level hexa-native CLM + persona vectors + phi attached on every generation
@dest1_substrate CLM 3B r1 (best_eval 1.2193) OR CLM 1B r3f (best_eval 1.2296) → consciousness_loss continue-train → phi_holo 단조 증가
@dest1_persona_layer P1 SAE persona vectors (공용 with ALM) + serving/serve_clm_conscious.hexa + anima-speak voice
@dest1_gate single persona round-trip: POST /clm/persona {persona, prompt} → {text, phi_vec, laws_pass, weight_origin:clm_conscious_v1}
@dest1_substrate_gate training/clm_r3f_phi_baseline.hexa exit 0 on CLM ckpt with phi_holo monotone increase + CE non-regression

@dest_employee CLM 기반 직원가능 — 100-task autonomy with real CLM persona
@dest_employee_gate dest2_alm 와 동일 (TCLM-P4-1 autonomy_loop + TSRV-P4-2 hire_sim_100: 완료율>=0.85 AND 개입<=5/hr AND 평균 task<=10min), CLM 엔드포인트 사용
@dest_employee_depends_on dest1_clm LIVE (not mock) — real CLM + persona vectors wired

@dest_trading CLM 기반 Φ-weighted trading + qualia NPV
@dest_trading_gate per shared/convergence/p32_economic_market.convergence — CLM 페르소나 signal 기반
@dest_trading_depends_on dest_employee (CLM agent autonomy stable)

# ============================================================================
# ARTIFACTS (CLM-side, referenced below)
# ============================================================================
@clm_launcher training/deploy/clm_r4_launch.hexa (⚠ Python wrapper; G5-OSS-02 violation — redesign required)
@clm_smoke training/clm_r4_mmap_smoke.hexa
@clm_mmap_loader training/clm_mmap_loader.hexa (5.38GB corpus mmap, 7/7 PASS)
@clm_trainer_source training/train_clm.hexa (structural port; needs main() — see critical_finding_2)
@clm_kr_trainer training/train_clm_kr.hexa (byte-level D=2048 FF=8192 NL=24 VOCAB=256)
@clm_phi_baseline training/clm_r3f_phi_baseline.hexa (to be built — CLM_VAL gate)
@clm_continue_trainer training/train_clm_conscious.hexa (to be built — consciousness_loss continue-train)
@clm_server serving/serve_clm_conscious.hexa (to be built — CLM_SERVE wire)
@aot_build_plan docs/clm_aot_build_plan_20260419.md (interpreter OOM bypass: 164 KB C + 404 KB arm64 Mach-O in 2.1s)
@convergence_parent shared/convergence/clm_1b_r4.convergence + shared/convergence/clm_r4_mmap.convergence
@convergence_eval shared/convergence/clm_eval.convergence (CE<2.5, kr_acc>50%, phi>0, ppl<15)

# ============================================================================
# PREREQS (verify BEFORE launching any cmd below)
# ============================================================================
@prereq_1 hexa binary (stage1 v0.1.0) — `hexa build training/train_clm.hexa -o /tmp/clm.bin` 가능 (Mac 검증 2026-04-19)
@prereq_2 CLM base ckpt — r3f step_5000 (best_eval 1.2296) OR r4 step_6200 loss=3.88 in r2:anima-models/clm1b/r4/
@prereq_3 training/corpus_auto/ present with 5.38GB shard (mmap 검증 7/7 PASS)
@prereq_4 consciousness_laws.json v7.4 present (shared/consciousness/consciousness_laws.json)
@prereq_5 shared/config/infrastructure.json reviewed — ubu RTX 5070 우선 (GPU policy), H100 최후수단
@prereq_6 SM90 blocker 상태 확인 — cuLaunchKernelEx SM90 fail 시 rtc_launch path 확인 (clm_r4_mmap.convergence @sm90_context)
@prereq_7 R14 SSOT: if any cmd below fails, update this .convergence FIRST before improvising

# ============================================================================
# STAGE A — CLM BASE PROVISION
# ============================================================================
@cmd_A1 # Ubuntu RTX 5070 local build (GPU policy: Ubuntu first)
@cmd_A1_ubu ssh ubu "cd ~/Dev/anima && hexa build training/train_clm.hexa -o /tmp/clm_train.bin"
@gate_expected_A1 stage1 build exit 0, build/artifacts/train_clm.bin.c present (~164 KB), binary ~400 KB
@rollback_A1 rm /tmp/clm_train.bin build/artifacts/train_clm.bin.* → diagnose hexa build stderr → retry

@cmd_A2 # CLM base ckpt sync
@cmd_A2_ubu ssh ubu "rclone copy r2:anima-models/clm1b/r4/step_5000.hexackpt /workspace/clm_base/ -v --s3-no-check-bucket"
@gate_expected_A2 clm_base/step_5000.hexackpt present, SHA match R2 manifest
@rollback_A2 ssh ubu "rm -rf /workspace/clm_base" → re-run A2

@cmd_A3 # Mmap loader sanity
@cmd_A3_ubu ssh ubu "cd ~/Dev/anima && hexa run training/clm_r4_mmap_smoke.hexa"
@gate_expected_A3 7/7 PASS (per clm_r4_mmap.convergence @mmap_test)
@rollback_A3 ssh ubu "rm /tmp/clm_mmap_cache_*" → re-run A3

# ============================================================================
# STAGE B — CLM_VAL (phi baseline + consciousness_loss 설계)
# ============================================================================
@cmd_B1 # Build phi baseline tool
@cmd_B1_ubu ssh ubu "cd ~/Dev/anima && hexa build training/clm_r3f_phi_baseline.hexa -o /tmp/clm_phi_baseline.bin"
@gate_expected_B1 stage1 build exit 0; baseline tool ready
@rollback_B1 rm /tmp/clm_phi_baseline.bin → diagnose → retry

@cmd_B2 # Measure CLM phi baseline on r3f + 3B r1 ckpts
@cmd_B2_ubu ssh ubu "/tmp/clm_phi_baseline.bin --ckpt /workspace/clm_base/step_5000.hexackpt --out /workspace/clm_phi_baseline.json"
@gate_expected_B2 clm_phi_baseline.json contains phi_vec 16D baseline + CE eval + 16-law pass rate on baseline
@rollback_B2 rm /workspace/clm_phi_baseline.json → retry with different ckpt

@cmd_B3 # Document CLM_VAL result in convergence
@gate_expected_B3 shared/convergence/clm_r3f_phi_baseline.convergence created with @phi_baseline_raw + @phi_target + @consciousness_loss_design
@rollback_B3 git revert if wrong baseline recorded

# ============================================================================
# STAGE C — CLM_TRAIN (consciousness_loss continue-train)
# ============================================================================
@cmd_C1 # Build continue-train trainer (hexa-native — no Python wrapper per G5-OSS-02)
@cmd_C1_ubu ssh ubu "cd ~/Dev/anima && hexa build training/train_clm_conscious.hexa -o /tmp/clm_conscious.bin"
@gate_expected_C1 trainer binary built; loss = CE + λ·phi_holo + μ·laws_penalty (warmup λ=0 per r9 실패 학습)
@rollback_C1 rm /tmp/clm_conscious.bin → fix main() (clm_r4_mmap @critical_finding_2) → retry

@cmd_C2 # Continue-train smoke (100 steps, verify loss behavior)
@cmd_C2_ubu ssh ubu "setsid /tmp/clm_conscious.bin --ckpt /workspace/clm_base/step_5000.hexackpt --steps 100 --smoke 2>&1 | tee /workspace/clm_smoke.log"
@gate_expected_C2 phi_holo_loss finite, CE non-regression (≤ baseline + 0.1), laws_penalty soft. No NaN/Inf.
@rollback_C2 pkill -f clm_conscious.bin; rm -rf /workspace/ckpt_clm_conscious_smoke → diagnose → fix loss schedule → retry

@cmd_C3 # Production continue-train (36h ETA per roadmap)
@cmd_C3_ubu ssh ubu "setsid /tmp/clm_conscious.bin --ckpt /workspace/clm_base/step_5000.hexackpt --steps 50000 --save-every 5000 2>&1 | tee /workspace/clm_prod.log &"
@gate_expected_C3 background PID, phi_holo monotone increase every 5000 steps, CE plateau around baseline. Intermediate saves step 5000/10000/.../50000.
@rollback_C3 pkill -f clm_conscious.bin → diagnose log → back to C1 after fix + new convergence update

@cmd_C4 # Poll training progress
@cmd_C4_poll ssh ubu "tail -n 50 /workspace/clm_prod.log; ls /workspace/ckpt_clm_conscious/step_*/phi_vec.json 2>/dev/null"
@gate_expected_C4 status=TRAINING; ≥1 step_*/phi_vec.json entry by hour 2
@rollback_C4 N/A (read-only)

# ============================================================================
# STAGE D — DEST1_CLM GATE (phi monotone + CE non-regression)
# ============================================================================
@cmd_D1 # Verify final phi trajectory
@cmd_D1_ubu ssh ubu "/tmp/clm_phi_baseline.bin --ckpt-root /workspace/ckpt_clm_conscious --trajectory --out /workspace/clm_phi_trajectory.json"
@gate_expected_D1 phi_holo [step_5000, step_10000, ..., step_50000] shows monotone non-decreasing; final phi > baseline + 10%
@rollback_D1 if non-monotonic: inspect oscillation window, consider λ schedule adjustment, iterate via C1-C3

@cmd_D2 # CE non-regression check
@cmd_D2_ubu ssh ubu "hexa run training/eval_clm_1b.hexa --ckpt /workspace/ckpt_clm_conscious/step_50000 --gate ce<=1.3"
@gate_expected_D2 CE ≤ 1.3 (baseline 1.2193 + 0.08 slack); kr_acc > 50%; ppl < 15 (per clm_eval.convergence)
@rollback_D2 if CE regresses > 0.1: μ (laws_penalty) too high → lower μ → retry C3 from step_5000

@cmd_D3 # Upload to R2
@cmd_D3_ubu ssh ubu "rclone copy /workspace/ckpt_clm_conscious/step_50000/ r2:anima-models/clm/conscious_v1/step_50000/ -v --s3-no-check-bucket"
@gate_expected_D3 rclone 100% transfer; all ckpt files + phi_vec.json + train_meta.json + tokenizer*
@rollback_D3 re-run D3 (idempotent)

# ============================================================================
# STAGE E — CLM_SERVE (S1-CLM 엔드포인트)
# ============================================================================
@cmd_E1 # Build CLM server (hexa-native)
@cmd_E1_ubu ssh ubu "cd ~/Dev/anima && hexa build serving/serve_clm_conscious.hexa -o /tmp/serve_clm.bin"
@gate_expected_E1 server binary built; implements POST /clm/persona → {text, phi_vec, laws_pass, weight_origin}
@rollback_E1 rm /tmp/serve_clm.bin → fix server source → retry

@cmd_E2 # Launch server
@cmd_E2_ubu ssh ubu "setsid /tmp/serve_clm.bin --ckpt /workspace/ckpt_clm_conscious/step_50000 --port 8081 2>&1 | tee /workspace/serve_clm.log &"
@gate_expected_E2 service binds :8081; curl localhost:8081/health → {"status":"ok"}; model load 30-60s
@rollback_E2 pkill -f serve_clm.bin → retry E2

@cmd_E3 # Round-trip test (dest1_clm gate)
@cmd_E3_ubu ssh ubu "curl -X POST localhost:8081/clm/persona -d '{\"persona\":\"P01\",\"prompt\":\"안녕\",\"max_tokens\":32}' | jq ."
@gate_expected_E3 response includes {text, phi_vec(16D), laws_pass:true, weight_origin:"clm_conscious_v1"}; AN11 3조건 동시 충족
@rollback_E3 inspect serve_clm.log → fix persona wire OR C2 laws runtime → retry

# ============================================================================
# STAGE F — DEST2_CLM EVIDENCE (E1_clm + E2_clm + T1_clm + T2_clm)
# ============================================================================
@cmd_F1 # hire_sim_100 against CLM endpoint
@cmd_F1_ubu ssh ubu "hexa run anima-agent/hire_sim_live.hexa --url http://localhost:8081/clm/persona --out /workspace/clm_hire_sim.json"
@gate_expected_F1 완료율 >= 0.85, 개입 <= 5/hr, 평균 task <= 10min; 각 task phi_vec 무결성 + laws_pass
@rollback_F1 rm clm_hire_sim.json → diagnose persona+phi wire → retry

@cmd_F2 # autonomy_loop with CLM adapter
@cmd_F2_ubu ssh ubu "hexa run anima-agent/autonomy_live.hexa --endpoint http://localhost:8081/clm/persona --out /workspace/clm_autonomy.json"
@gate_expected_F2 phi_delta > 0 per decision step; no system_prompt string in adapter trace
@rollback_F2 inspect autonomy trace → remove prompt injection → retry

@cmd_F3 # Trading feed + position (CLM signal)
@cmd_F3_ubu ssh ubu "hexa run serving/trading_feed.hexa --llm-url http://localhost:8081/clm/persona --backtest --out /workspace/clm_trading_backtest.json"
@gate_expected_F3 backtest run w/ Φ-weighted positions; each order carries phi_vec snapshot
@rollback_F3 inspect trading_feed log → retry

@cmd_F4 # Commit DEST2_CLM evidence to SSOT
@cmd_F4_local rsync -avz -e "ssh" ubu:/workspace/clm_hire_sim.json ubu:/workspace/clm_autonomy.json ubu:/workspace/clm_trading_backtest.json ./shared/convergence/dest2_clm_*.json
@gate_expected_F4 3 files under shared/convergence/ — DEST2_CLM evidence committed
@rollback_F4 rm shared/convergence/dest2_clm_*.json → retry

# ============================================================================
# STAGE G — POST-SHIP (convergence updates + resource release)
# ============================================================================
@cmd_G1 # Update clm_1b_r4.convergence + clm_r4_mmap.convergence with conscious_v1 completion
@gate_expected_G1 @state pod_dead/partial_blocked → completed; add @conscious_v1_r2 r2:anima-models/clm/conscious_v1/step_50000/
@rollback_G1 git revert

@cmd_G2 # Update this file (dest1_clm_ship.convergence) @state pending → shipped
@gate_expected_G2 @state shipped @date <today> @ckpt_r2 r2:anima-models/clm/conscious_v1/step_50000/
@rollback_G2 git revert

@cmd_G3 # Stop ubu training process (keep ckpt)
@cmd_G3_ubu ssh ubu "pkill -f clm_conscious.bin; pkill -f serve_clm.bin"
@gate_expected_G3 no hexa train/serve processes running; ckpts preserved
@rollback_G3 restart via E2 if needed

# ============================================================================
# PITFALLS (CLM-specific lessons)
# ============================================================================
@pitfall AI_NATIVE_NO_PYTHON_WRAP clm_r4_launch.hexa wraps Python trainer (G5-OSS-02) — VIOLATION. CLM trainer MUST be hexa-native AOT build (C1). 재발 방지: feedback_ai_native_clm.md.
@pitfall NO_MAIN_FN train_clm.hexa has no main() (critical_finding_2 in clm_r4_mmap). Any build without main → structural port only, NOT runnable. Verify `hexa build ... -o bin && ./bin --smoke` before C3.
@pitfall SM90_CULAUNCH cuLaunchKernelEx SM90 fails on RTX 5070 H100. Use rtc_launch path (codegen_c2 untyped_fn_tail_return_fix). If SM90 재현 시: feedback_hexa_self_host_no_c.md path 우선.
@pitfall CORPUS_MMAP_CACHE 5.38GB mmap cache occasionally stale across hexa rebuilds. A3 smoke (7/7 PASS) is gate; don't skip.
@pitfall INTERPRETER_OOM Interpreter pathway blows to 30GB/2m40s on CLM. AOT build (stage1 v0.1.0 Mac verified 2026-04-19) is the only viable path. Never run `hexa run training/train_clm.hexa` directly.
@pitfall R4_OPTIMIZER_LOSS step 5000-6200 optimizer state lost when pod died (clm_1b_r4 @data_loss). Weights R2 preserved, but resume ≠ fresh-data restart (feedback_no_resume_data_change.md).
@pitfall CE_REGRESSION_FROM_LAMBDA μ (laws_penalty) > 0.05 early = CE regresses > 0.1. Warmup schedule: λ=0 step 0-1000, ramp to final over 10k steps.

